Class MaterialTabHelper

    MoodockTabHelper

    public abstract class MaterialTabHelper
extends SliderTabHelper
    MaterialTabHelper is a slider helper class for your project that:

    Inherited: save/load/reset the extra settings preferences. save/load/reset the utils preferences. Get/Set an util preference. Get the previous tabview position of the actual position. save/load/reset the base settings preferences. Get/Set a setting preference.
